427
00:29:22,770 --> 00:29:24,139
Fokus saja dengan pelatihanmu.

428
00:29:25,369 --> 00:29:26,440
Mengerti?

429
00:29:28,309 --> 00:29:29,539
Lekas makan.

430
00:29:43,389 --> 00:29:46,530
