434
00:29:58,069 --> 00:29:59,270
Kenapa kalian bisa pulang bersama?

435
00:29:59,710 --> 00:30:02,879
Universitas mengumumkan penerimaan O Dol,

436
00:30:03,039 --> 00:30:04,940
